stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> ContextBuild
    
    ContextBuild: Context Injection
    note right of ContextBuild
        - Read user_profiles
        - Aggregate behavior_logs
        - Vector search user_embeddings
    end note
    
    ContextBuild --> LoopStart
    
    LoopStart --> Thought
    
    Thought: Thought: Analyze problem
    note right of Thought
        LLM reasons about what to do
    end note
    
    Thought --> DecisionCheck{Action needed?}
    
    DecisionCheck --> FinalAnswer: No more tools
    DecisionCheck --> ToolCall: Yes
    
    ToolCall: Tool Call
    note right of ToolCall
        - Validate input schema
        - Check sensitive (approval?)
        - Execute tool
    end note
    
    ToolCall --> Observation
    
    Observation: Observation: Tool result
    Observation --> IterCheck
    
    IterCheck{Iteration < 4?}
    IterCheck --> Thought: Yes
    IterCheck --> LoopBreaker: No
    
    LoopBreaker: Loop Breaker
    note right of LoopBreaker
        - Log behavior
        - Return fallback message
    end note
    
    FinalAnswer: Final Answer
    note right of FinalAnswer
        - Format with tone
        - Personalize if possible
        - Log to conversation_history
    end note
    
    FinalAnswer --> LogBehavior
    LoopBreaker --> LogBehavior
    
    LogBehavior: Log behavior
    LogBehavior --> [*]
